<abstract>New York City Parking Lots, 2022 is a polygon theme representing parking lots greater than 2,000 square feet in New York City as of 2022. This dataset is part of the 2022 NYC Planimetric Database.  Further information can be found here.  https://github.com/CityOfNewYork/nyc-planimetrics/blob/main/Capture_Rules.md  Columbia library staff accessed this data in April of 2026 and has provided it in the geopackage format.
		</abstract>
		<purpose>To support city agency operational requirements and public data access. </purpose>
	</descript>
